<h1>About Us</h1>

<div class="flex-container reviews-page">

    <!-- Sidebar Info Panel -->
    <aside class="cart-sidebar">
        <h2>About Our Tech Mall</h2>

        <h3>Our History</h3>
        <p>We have been providing the best prices on technology products since 2010. Our founder Thomas A. Anderson has been dedicated to this mission since the beginning and has a burning passion for technology!</p>

        <h3>Mission & Vision</h3>
        <p>We aim to give you the best shopping experience either here online or in store!</p>

        <h3>Contact Info</h3>
        <p>
            Email: email@email.com<br />
            Phone: 01135 556789<br />
            Address: 123 Tech Ave, Silicon City
        </p>

