    <!-- Grid of Informational Cards -->
    <div class="review-grid">

        <div class="product-card">
            <h3>Management</h3>
            <p>Our experienced leadership team consists of tech professionals from every vertical. Need help? Ask us a question!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <h3>Services Offered</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Tech Support: On site help for product setup and troubleshooting.</li>
                <li>Gadget Repair: In house repair services for electronics and gadgets.</li>
                <li>Free WiFi: High speed WiFi available throughout the mall.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <h3>Sustainability</h3>
            <p>Our mall is committed to sustainability through energy efficient lighting, responsible ewaste recycling programs, and promoting eco friendly tech products.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
            <h3>Virtual Store Tours</h3>
            <p>Explore our tech mall remotely with our interactive 3D virtual store tours. (COMING SOON)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card">
